<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="lie-in">lie in</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>在于</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The value of diamond lies in its hardness.
钻石的价值在于它质地坚硬。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She told me that happiness lies in helping others to be happy.
她告诉我快乐的真谛在于帮助他人获得快乐。</p></div></div>